OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan admits 'deplorable'    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBradley Lowery taunt       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Sheffield Wednesday fan who used a   
OL,6, photo of Bradley Lowery to taunt       
OL,7, opposition supporters has admitted a   
OL,8, public order offence.                  
OL,10,FDale Houghton, 31, was pictured        
OL,11,Flaughing as he brandished the image of 
OL,12,Fthe six-year-old during a match against
OL,13,FSunderland - the team Bradley supported
OL,14,Fbefore he died of cancer in 2017.      
OL,16,FHe pleaded guilty at Sheffield         
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court on Monday.          
OL,19,FDistrict judge James Gould described   
OL,20,Fhis actions as "utterly deplorable".   
